# CRX signing keys — NEVER commit. The production key is the one thing
# you can't lose. Stored as a GitHub Actions secret + offline encrypted backup.
*.pem
*.pem.gpg
bastio-extension.pem
bastio-extension.pem.gpg

# Local-only working files. Belt-and-suspenders so internal notes,
# Claude Code project memory, or workspace-private design docs never
# accidentally land in this public repo.
.claude/
CLAUDE.md
.work/
.cursor/
.aider*

# Release artifacts at repo root (the build pipeline writes into release/,
# but these patterns catch stray manual zips).
*.crx
*.zip
*.xpi
